attributionInfo.brokerName: Home Sweet Home Realty by Laurie LaMotte, LLC

data.description: This stunning home located in the Trent Woods area of New Bern, North Carolina is sure to take your breath away! Situated on a corner lot, this property boasts almost three-quarters of an acre of land. With three bedrooms on the main level and two additional bedrooms plus a bonus room of 350 square feet, there is plenty of space for everyone. The eat-in kitchen is a chef's dream with quartz countertops, Viking and Gaggenau appliances, and ample storage space.The home features not one, but two living areas, one of which includes a cozy fireplace, while the other is perfect for more formal entertaining. Both rooms and the formal dining area overlook the spacious deck with retractable awning and private backyard. The walk-in attic provides plenty of storage space, while the bonus room is currently used as a craft room.This energy-efficient home is equipped with two geothermal units for heating and is hooked up to natural gas. It also includes a Renai hot water heater and gas dryer. The home automation/security system allows you to control the thermostat and lights from your smartphone. The crawl space has been encapsulated for added protection, and the back yard is newly fenced in using two neighbor fences.Finally, the best part of this home is the newer hot tub with all the bells and whistles, including Bluetooth and an easy lift cover system. There is also plenty of concrete parking for an RV, boat, or extra cars. This property is protected by a warranty through 2-10 Home Buyers Warranty and is available for purchase at closing. Don't miss out on the opportunity to call this amazing property your new home!
